<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Language Reference on UPPAAL Documentation</title><link>/language-reference/</link><description>Recent content in Language Reference on UPPAAL Documentation</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="/language-reference/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Reserved Keywords</title><link>/language-reference/reserved-keywords/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/language-reference/reserved-keywords/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The reserved keywords that should not be used as &lt;a href="/language-reference/expressions/identifiers/"&gt;identifier names&lt;/a&gt; when defining systems are: &lt;tt&gt;chan&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;clock&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;double&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;bool&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;int&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;commit&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;const&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;urgent&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;broadcast&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;init&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;process&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;state&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;invariant&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;location&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;guard&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;sync&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;assign&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;system&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;trans&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;deadlock&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;and&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;or&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;not&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;imply&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;true&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;false&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;for&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;forall&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;exists&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;while&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;do&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;if&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;else&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;return&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;typedef&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;struct&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;rate&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;before_update&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;after_update&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;meta&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;priority&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;progress&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;scalar&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;select&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;void&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;default&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;string&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;minE&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;maxE&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;Pr&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following keywords are reserved for future use: &lt;tt&gt;switch&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;case&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;continue&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;break&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;enum&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>